:0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2384ae31f9e49be83e9c4518d1d25e8bae24edf2","tid":1624111,"uid":53128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"點會唔做手腳DQ"},{"pid":"5d7ec3028b64ebd65d7079240d30082a74806f8e","tid":1624111,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba9a123fbc73be6c5cfb109d41a8ad0a4b3b8824","tid":1624111,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:00:11.000Z","msg":"基本法確認書都出埋<br />\n仲議咩會抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"都仲可以有好多同路人係唔會被dq<br />\n唔通你寧願所以資源都比建制派攞曬,然後用黎收買人心？<br />\n<br />\n宜家我地做既抗爭係任何一個戰場都唔可以放棄"},{"pid":"c251b9d29da4e50538fa60eae3f86c8f240a7c60","tid":1624111,"uid":277912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:50:15.000Z","msg":"你信特衰政府真係會俾你選？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4eb70ecbe102622734e41efa7c38126793cf85","tid":1624111,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"港共驚區選輸嘅話<br />\n佢可以以公眾安全為理由格硬無限期延後<br />\nDQ大部分支持民主嘅候選人<br />\n我哋先避免第一個情況出現<br />\n要逼港共大規模DQ嘅時候咪繼續請美國制裁同街頭抗爭"}]}